<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٤٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْعَذَابِ}</span> ... مِنَ الجَرَادِ، وَالقُمَّلِ، وَالضَّفَادِعِ، وَنَحْوِهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السَّاحِرُ}</span> ... العَالِمُ <span class="c2">(وَكَانَ السَّاحِرُ فِيهِمْ عَظِيمًا يُوَقِّرُونَهُ، وَلَمْ يَكُنْ صِفَةَ ذَمٍّ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِمَا عَهِدَ عِندَكَ}</span> ... بِعَهْدِهِ الَّذِي عَهِدَ إِلَيْكَ، وَمَا خَصَّكَ بِهِ مِنَ الفَضَائِلِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَنكُثُونَ}</span> ... يَغْدِرُونَ، وَيُصِرُّونَ عَلَى الكُفْرِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَهِينٌ}</span> ... ضَعِيفٌ لَا عِزَّ لَهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا يَكَادُ يُبِينُ}</span> ... لَا يَكَادُ يُفْصِحُ فِي كَلَامِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُقْتَرِنِينَ}</span> ... مَقْرُونِينَ مَعَهُ يُصَدِّقُونَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَاسْتَخَفَّ قَوْمَهُ}</span> ... اسْتَخَفَّ بِعُقُولِهِمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آسَفُونَا}</span> ... أَغْضَبُونَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَلَفًا}</span> ... قُدْوَةً لِمَنْ يَعْمَلُ مِثْلَ عَمَلِهِمْ؛ فَيَسْتَحِقُّ العُقُوبَةَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَثَلًا}</span> ... عِظَةً، وَعِبْرَةً.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَصِدُّونَ}</span> ... يَضَجُّونَ، وَيَصِيحُونَ، فَرَحًا، وَجَذَلًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَصِمُونَ}</span> ... شَدِيدُو الخُصُومَةِ بِالبَاطِلِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٥٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَثَلًا}</span> ... عِبْرَةً، وَآيَةً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَجَعَلْنَا مِنكُم}</span> ... لَجَعَلْنَا بَدَلَكُمْ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>